# Dockerignore for the Tilt dev image (dev/provider.Dockerfile).
#
# BuildKit prefers <dockerfile>.dockerignore over the top-level .dockerignore.
# The dev image COPYs the host-built bin/provider, so - unlike the production
# build - we must NOT exclude bin here. Tilt further narrows the context via
# only=['bin/provider'], so everything else is irrelevant to this image.
.git
.github
.gitignore
cover.out
provider-kubeai
